ephropathy.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/74577/', '', 'Sorbitol, Sulfamethizole, Sodium citrate, Magnesium citrate, Sodium bicarbonate, Sodium chloride, Chlorhexidine, Alvimopan, Sorbitol, Tegaserod, Naloxegol, More', 'Ethiodized oil, Iopanoic acid, Tyropanoic acid, Iopodic acid', 1767369485);
